title: alt.sex.stories.moderated archives 1997-2007
description:
A new year, another release of the assm archive.

Around 1975 pornographic novellas from the alt.sex.stories.moderated archive for 2007, provided here in a self-extracting RAR-archive (win32). ** You can also use your favourite unrar application to unpack these on any supported platform (linux, bsd, osx, etc) -- YOU DON&#039;T HAVE TO RUN THE SELF-EXTRACTOR SO DON&#039;T COMPLAIN ABOUT THE EXECUTABLE, YOU IDIOT **

Notes:
 * Also included are all the previous archives, from 1997 and on.

 * All files are regular text files, you can open them in a text editor or your web browser.

 * I have not modified any files in the 2007 archive (don&#039;t recall for the early ones), so if you use the included HTML files note that these links to the internet assm archive, not your local files!
